OL,3,CPair sentenced for felling village
OL,4,CChristmas tree planted as war memorial
OL,6,FWatch the moment the tree was cut down
OL,7,Fon the night of 10 December 2025.
OL,8,FCredit: Durham Constabulary
OL,10,FTwo men have been sentenced after
OL,11,Fcutting down a Christmas tree in a
OL,12,FCounty Durham village which had been
OL,13,Fplanted as a World War One memorial.
OL,15,FThe 22ft tree had stood in the centre
OL,16,Fof Shotton Colliery for the last ten
OL,17,Fyears, but was felled on 10 December
OL,18,F2025, just hours after a ceremony to
OL,19,Fturn on the Christmas lights.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
