PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784814496
OL,3,CPair sentenced for felling village
OL,4,CChristmas tree planted as war memorial
OL,6,FPolice were alerted to the incident
OL,7,Fwhich happened at around 10.50pm, and
OL,8,Flaunched an investigation which led to
OL,9,Fthe pair's arrest.
OL,11,FOfficers discovered that Dylan
OL,12,FMcNamara, 26, used a bow saw to cut
OL,13,Fthe tree down, while his friend, 28-
OL,14,Fyear-old Dominic Radcliffe, acted as a
OL,15,Flookout.
OL,17,FDuring a search of McNamara's
OL,18,Fpartner's house in Shotton, officers
OL,19,Ffound a bow saw hidden behind the
OL,20,Ffridge freezer.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784814496
OL,3,CPair sentenced for felling village
OL,4,CChristmas tree planted as war memorial
OL,6,FThe pair were both charged with
OL,7,Fcriminal damage, which they admitted.
OL,9,FAt a court hearing on Monday (20
OL,10,FJuly), Radcliffe was given an eight-
OL,11,Fweek suspended prison sentence, and
OL,12,Fordered to carry out 100 hours of
OL,13,Funpaid work.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, McNamara was sentenced at a
OL,16,Fseparate hearing last month, and given
OL,17,Fa ten-week suspended prison sentence,
OL,18,Fand ordered to carry out 200 hours of
OL,19,Funpaid work.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
