FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784814496
OL,3,CPair sentenced for felling village
OL,4,CChristmas tree planted as war memorial
OL,6,FPC David Allan and PCSO Katie McKee,
OL,7,Ffrom Peterlee Neighbourhood Police
OL,8,FTeam, said: "The tree was not only a
OL,9,Ffestive decoration, but a longstanding
OL,10,Fsymbol in the village of remembrance,
OL,11,Funity, and respect for those who
OL,12,Fserved.
OL,14,F"The felling of the tree caused
OL,15,Fsignificant hurt, upset, and
OL,16,Fdisappointment among residents.
OL,18,F"McNamara and Radcliffe showed
OL,19,Fabsolutely no consideration for these
OL,20,Fresidents when they committed this
OL,21,Futterly mindless act of vandalism.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784814496
OL,3,CPair sentenced for felling village
OL,4,CChristmas tree planted as war memorial
OL,6,F"We hope this case shows that
OL,7,Fbehaviour like this will not be
OL,8,Ftolerated within our communities, and
OL,9,Fthat action will be taken against
OL,10,Fthose who commit such offences."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
